reviewText: I AM Mary Elizabeth Stevens and I think this is the BEST workout video ever made.
This video gives you toned thighs in a short time.  Love it!

I absolutely love this tape. You get a great workout in little time, and you see results.
I found it to be a bit challenging but doable.

I purchased this video from a local thrift shop and almost didn't get it. Boyyyyyyy would that have been a big mistake. Thin Thighs was one of the smartest purchases I've made. This workout Rocks!!! You want Thin Thighs ladies?.... Make a smart purchase and order Thin Thighs or check your local thrift shop, you might just luck up.
Very quick and targeted workout. Your thighs will burn the next day and progress follows quickly. I definately recommend it!
